name: Daniel Ham
description: I love poetry, books, walks on the beach and cozy candlelight dinners. I enjoy movies, television, music, traveling, the desert, the quietness of the mountains, the ocean, sunrises and sunsets. A nonsmoker/drinker, not into drugs (don’t need them; I live in a natural high). I believe in enjoying the good and Quite life . I have a healthy attitude about God and the Bible.
